{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From the creators of Synth Riders comes <strong>FINAL FURY</strong>, a VR fighting game that redefines stepping into the ring. Face off against the galaxy\u2019s fiercest fighters\u2014offline or across the world with rollback netcode. This isn\u2019t some button-pushing battle. Every punch, block, and special attack is powered by YOUR movement.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>FINAL FURY</strong> is more than a fighting game\u2014this is a VR fighting game, done right.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u200e\u3164</strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782760/extras/steam_gameplay_loop_1.gif?t=1738089867\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782760/extras/headline1.png?t=1738089867\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Feel like a fighter</strong>\u00a0as YOU step into the arena. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Innovative VR combat</strong>, combining arcade fighting mechanics with physical gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Expanding roster of fighters</strong>, each boasting unique move sets, arenas, and personalities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Spar Solo</strong>\u00a0in Single-player battles against CPU opponents.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Compete Online</strong>\u00a0with cross-platform play and rollback netcode.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Heart-pumping original soundtrack</strong>\u00a0composed by Zardonic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782760/extras/image2.png?t=1738089867\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782760/extras/headline2.png?t=1738089867\" /><strong>FINAL FURY</strong>\u00a0isn\u2019t just about picking a fighter and learning their moves\u2014BECOME the fighter! Feel the adrenaline as you unleash your\u00a0FINAL FURY\u00a0in immersive VR battles where you are the hero. Whether you\u2019re rushing down, footsie-ing, or action-canceling your way to victory,\u00a0<strong>FINAL FURY</strong>\u00a0offers a skill curve that\u2019s easy to pick up and challenging to master.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782760/extras/steam_showdowns_loop_2.gif?t=1738089867\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782760/extras/headline3.png?t=1738089867\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience Intense fights as you come to blows in first person, then get pumped as you see ground-pounding finishers and grapples unfold from a third-person perspective. Between the breathtaking arenas and an adrenaline-soaked soundtrack from Zardonic (SUPERHOT: MIND CONTROL DELETE), you\u2019ve got a front row seat to the sweat-inducing fury!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u200e\u3164</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782760/extras/social.png?t=1738089867\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Join the official <strong>FINAL FURY</strong> Discord to learn more about community tournaments, the latest <strong>FINAL FURY</strong> news, and insights straight from the dev team! This fight\u2019s just getting started!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782760/extras/discord_green.png?t=1738089867\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.stea